*** What is new in Cream 3.0.0

- switched to MySQL database
- possible Campsite integration where Cream manage Campsite subscriptions
- contacts management
- opportunities management
- tasks management
- external HTML forms for support and info requests
- new custom fields in support and info requests
- bill to and ship to addresses in customers
- some additional customer fields
- added view of related contacts, documents and tasks in the customer detail
- added view of related documents and tasks in the contact detail
- added view of related documents and tasks in the campaign detail
- added view of related documents in the sales order detail
- many new options
- import of Newsletter Subscriptions
- changed look of user interface
- added paginating for all lists
- fixed some bugs

